data.description: A sociological examination of the influence of rurality and place on gender and sexual performances, norms, and identities in rural geographies.
data.title: GENDER AND SEXUALITY IN RURAL PLACES

data.description: Global, interdisciplinary, social science-oriented analysis of gender, race, class and sexuality in relationship to social institutions and movements for social change. Focus on gender and women in institutions such as education, the economy, the family, law, media, medicine, and politics.
data.title: GENDER, WOMEN, AND SOCIETY IN GLOBAL PERSPECTIVE
